<header class="flex justify-center bg-[#252422] text-[#fff9ef] h-20">
    <nav class="flex justify-between container px-5">
        <div class="hidden sm:flex items-center text-3xl text-[#fff9ef] logo-text">
            Sheetty
            <img src="sheetty-logo-compact.svg" width="40" class="ml-3">
        </div>

        <ul class="w-full flex flex-row gap-4 justify-between md:justify-end h-[80px] items-center">
            <li><a class="p-2 sm:px-5 block w-full h-full hover:bg-[#ff5e29] rounded-3xl"
                   href="#features">Features</a>
            </li>
            <li><a class="p-2 sm:px-5 block w-full h-full hover:bg-[#ff5e29] rounded-3xl"
                   href="#pricing">Pricing</a>
            </li>
            <li><a class="p-2 sm:px-5 block w-full h-full hover:bg-[#ff5e29] rounded-3xl"
                   href="https://app.sheetty.com/signin" target="_blank">Sign in</a>
            </li>
            <li><a
                    class="p-2 sm:px-5 block w-full h-full bg-[#ff5e29] rounded-3xl hover:brightness-125"
                    href="https://app.sheetty.com/signup"
                    target="_blank"
                    onclick="gtag_report_conversion('https://app.sheetty.com/signup')">Sign up</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>
</header>

<div class="container px-5 mx-auto">
    <section id="hero" class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center pt-10 mb-10">
        <div class="prose sm:prose-2xl text-center w-full p-2">
            <h1 style="margin-bottom: 0.2em">Track time <span class="blur-sm hover:blur-none cursor-none">🕑</span>
                like a <span class="text-6xl sm:text-9xl">Software Developer</span></h1>

            <p class="text-justify">Sheetty is a time tracking app that lets you use shortcuts, <code>ctrl+k</code>
                search bar and calendar-like
                widgets to reduce time spent timesh**ting. And makes it fun.</p>
            <p class="text-justify">It tracks your contracts, hours worked, money earned and maximum hours you can clock
                in.</p>
        </div>

        <a href="https://app.sheetty.com/signup" target="_blank"
           class="p-3 mt-5 rounded-3xl text-white text-2xl bg-[#ff5e29] hover:brightness-125 font-bold uppercase text-center"
           onclick="gtag_report_conversion('https://app.sheetty.com/signup')"
        >
            Start 90 Days Free Trial
        </a>
    </section>

    <section id="ribbon" class="grid grid-rows-1 grid-flow-row">
        <div class="w-[640px] mx-auto border-2 mb-10 border-[#ffcfbf] rounded hidden sm:block drop-shadow-xl">
            <video class="lg:w-full lg:h-full hover:cursor-pointer" controls poster="sheetty-fast-onboarding.png">
                <source src="sheetty-fast-onboarding.mp4" type="video/mp4"/>
                Your browser does not support the video tag.
            </video>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-row flex-wrap justify-between">
            <div class="prose sm:prose-2xl lg:w-[30%] mb-20">
                <h2>Quick Actions</h2>
                <p>
                    You can use mouse or shortcuts and quick actions to do the same thing faster. E.g. manage
                    your time tracking, navigate or export timesheets.
                </p>

                <img src="quick-actions.png" alt="quick actions" class="mx-auto"/>
            </div>

            <div class="prose sm:prose-2xl lg:w-[30%] mb-20">
                <h2>Hotkeys</h2>
                <p>
                    Press <code>alt + key</code> to navigate the app without moving your mouse.
                    E.g. alt-tab from your IDE to your browser, then press a combo of hotkeys to
                    quickly set up your time tracker for a new task. And then get back to work.
                </p>

                <img src="hotekeys.png" alt="hotkeys" class="mx-auto"/>
            </div>

            <div class="prose sm:prose-2xl lg:w-[30%]">
                <h2>Timesheet Editing</h2>
                <p>
                    You can use the Timeline View and simply drag blocks of time on it (like in a calendar
                    app), or go to the list view
                    and change your entries with a keyboard. You can always add entries manually
                    for any day using the calendar.
                </p>

                <img src="editing1.png" alt="timesheet editing" class="mx-auto"/>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>

<div class="bg-[#fff9ef] py-10 my-5">
    <div class="container px-5 mx-auto flex flex-col items-center">
        <div class="prose sm:prose-2xl mb-5">
            <h2>90 Days Free Trial</h2>
            <p>
                We offer a modern and simple time tracking tool. Sheetty has minimum features to do maximum
                work. Try it for <span class="font-bold">90 days for free</span>. No credit card required. No risk.
            </p>
        </div>

        <a href="https://app.sheetty.com/signup" target="_blank"
           class="p-3 mt-5 rounded-3xl text-white text-2xl bg-[#ff5e29] hover:brightness-125 font-bold uppercase text-center"
           onclick="gtag_report_conversion('https://app.sheetty.com/signup')"
        >
            Start 90 Days Free Trial
        </a>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container px-5 mx-auto">
    <section>
        <div class="sm:mb-10">
            <div class="prose sm:prose-2xl p-2 mb-5">
                <h2>Interactive Timeline</h2>
                <p>Effortlessly drag and drop time entries, just like in a calendar.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center text-[#fff9ef]">
                <video width="w-full h-[250px]" autoplay loop muted>
                    <source src="sheetty.mp4"/>
                </video>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex flex-row flex-wrap justify-between">
            <div class="lg:w-[30%] mb-5">
                <div class="flex flex-col">
                    <div class="prose sm:prose-2xl p-2 mb-5">
                        <h2>Smart Autocomplete</h2>
                        <p>Fuzzy search scoped to a single client allows you to quickly find recurring tasks.</p>
                    </div>

                    <img src="autocomplete.png" alt="autocomplete" class="mx-auto"/>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="lg:w-[30%]">
                <div class="flex flex-col justify-between">
                    <div class="prose sm:prose-2xl p-2 mb-5">
                        <h2>Parallel Tracking</h2>
                        <p>
                            Use your time more efficiently with an instant overview of all running time trackers. You
                            can quickly browse, discard or finish tasks without even changing your current context.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <img src="parallel-trackers.png" alt="parallel time tracking" class="mx-auto"/>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="lg:w-[30%] mb-5">
                <div class="flex flex-col">
                    <div class="prose sm:prose-2xl p-2 mb-5">
                        <h2>Quick Stats</h2>
                        <p>Your favourite statistics are always available. Just open up the drawer on the side</p>
                        <p>Track your earnings and hours worked for a client or a contract.</p>
                    </div>

                    <img src="quick-stats.png" alt="quick statistics" class="mx-auto"/>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</div>

<section class="bg-[#fff9ef] py-5">
    <div id="pricing" class="flex justify-center items-center flex-col">
        <div class="prose sm:prose-2xl px-5 text-center mb-10 w-full md:w-[35ch]">
            <h2>Pricing</h2>
            <p>Our pricing is simple and honest. We'll never sell your personal information to advertising agencies or
                any third parties.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="w-full sm:w-[600px]">
            <div class="bg-[#252422] text-[#fff9ef] md:rounded-3xl py-10 p-2 sm:p-20 text-center text-xl">
                <div class="mb-10">
                    <p class="mb-2 text-4xl">
                        <span class="font-bold mb-2">from 0,99 €*</span>
                    </p>
                    <p>per 30 days</p>
                </div>

                <div class="w-full flex justify-center px-5">
                    <ul class="text-left w-full sm:w-[300px] leading-10">
